title: Two British Idiots Escape A Haunted House | Alone In The Dark
description:
By day, Chris and Adam are video producers for GameSpot in the UK, but for one night only they took on the role of urban explorers searching for a lost family heirloom, as THQ Nordic invited them to a real-life Haunted House experience for their game Alone in the Dark.

Rigged up with body cameras and heart-rate monitors, watch as Chris, Adam and Lampy try their best to survive a terrifying night alone in a haunted house. What terrifying secrets lurk in the darkness, and can they escape? There's only one way to find out.
